title: Web Development Basics
description: Dive into the world of web development with this introductory course. Learn about HTML, CSS, and basic JavaScript.

title: Advanced Python Programming
description: Take your Python skills to the next level. Explore advanced concepts, algorithms, and real-world applications.

description: Master data analysis and machine learning with R. Get hands-on experience with real-world datasets.

description: Understand the principles of cloud computing and gain proficiency in AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud.

description: Design and develop mobile apps using React Native. Create cross-platform applications for iOS and Android.
